00:15.338 --> 00:17.405
Morning.

00:17.472 --> 00:18.505
Jesus.

00:19.157 --> 00:20.638
No... Daniel.

00:21.985 --> 00:23.178
I forgot you were here.

00:23.572 --> 00:26.437
I don't know how that's
possible, but I... did.

00:27.276 --> 00:28.604
I don't know why I drink.

00:28.672 --> 00:31.305
Don't like the high, and
I hate the hangover.

00:31.879 --> 00:32.952
What are you looking for?

00:33.210 --> 00:35.005
Time. You have the time?

00:35.476 --> 00:36.772
You have a watch.

00:36.838 --> 00:38.238
It's broken.

00:38.305 --> 00:39.605
I don't have the time.

00:39.672 --> 00:41.272
I have a phone that has the time.

00:42.117 --> 00:43.072
A phone?

00:43.138 --> 00:44.578
Yes.

00:45.598 --> 00:47.911
I saw a phone in the kitchen.

00:48.472 --> 00:50.138
In the drawer.

00:52.538 --> 00:55.672
The one with the, uh, i-ice-cream scooper.

01:00.799 --> 01:03.005
Okay, I'm definitely late.

01:03.901 --> 01:05.604
There's cereal.

01:05.672 --> 01:07.505
I don't think there's any milk.

01:07.572 --> 01:08.591
No problem.

01:08.779 --> 01:12.538
Sorry, the fridge isn't
perpetually stocked like mom's.

01:12.605 --> 01:15.038
See, the way I roll is...

01:15.105 --> 01:18.733
I don't eat. I don't eat. I don't eat.

01:20.038 --> 01:21.622
And then I eat shit.

01:22.045 --> 01:24.338
A lot of shit.

01:24.405 --> 01:26.405
Seems to be working.

01:30.705 --> 01:31.672
How's your bed?

01:33.872 --> 01:35.037
Airy.

01:35.805 --> 01:37.372
Oh, you need a key.

01:37.438 --> 01:39.172
I-i don't have to have a key.

01:39.238 --> 01:42.072
Yes, you do. People steal shit around here.

01:42.958 --> 01:44.872
That was the one problem I didn't have

01:44.938 --> 01:45.972
where I used to live.

01:46.038 --> 01:47.213
Mom's?

01:47.572 --> 01:49.005
The place before.

01:57.938 --> 01:59.572
You need some money?

02:00.643 --> 02:03.709
No, I just needed a place
to stay, Amantha...

02:04.105 --> 02:05.372
Temporarily.

02:05.438 --> 02:06.638
That's all.

02:09.172 --> 02:10.538
Well, have a great day.

02:12.332 --> 02:14.105
Yes, you too.

02:20.305 --> 02:21.897
Did Teddy say where Tawney was?

02:23.131 --> 02:24.605
He said he didn't know.

02:24.672 --> 02:26.038
Huh.

02:28.935 --> 02:30.902
I think it had something to do with Daniel.

02:32.302 --> 02:34.002
Is that right?

02:38.035 --> 02:39.402
Oh, and Amantha called.

02:40.243 --> 02:41.768
Said Daniel's staying with her now.

02:42.245 --> 02:43.410
Well, that's good to hear.

02:43.639 --> 02:44.755
Well, that is good to hear.

02:45.585 --> 02:47.768
But I wonder why Daniel just
up and went to Amantha's

02:47.835 --> 02:49.035
all of a sudden.

02:49.102 --> 02:50.868
That's curious, don't you think?

02:52.064 --> 02:53.434
I'm sure he had his reasons.

02:53.502 --> 02:55.758
And I wonder why you're lying to me, Ted.

02:57.768 --> 02:59.602
I'm not lying to you, Janet.

02:59.668 --> 03:02.357
Okay, maybe not, but you're
sure not telling me something.

03:04.142 --> 03:05.468
I asked him to leave.

03:06.316 --> 03:07.502
Why?

03:07.568 --> 03:09.321
Why would you do that?

03:10.468 --> 03:12.335
And I asked him to tell you the reason.

03:12.402 --> 03:13.502
Well, he didn't.

03:13.568 --> 03:15.168
What was the reason, Ted?

03:16.512 --> 03:18.268
Daniel assaulted Teddy.

03:19.735 --> 03:20.668
What?

03:21.173 --> 03:22.009
He choked him out.

03:22.111 --> 03:23.224
Choked him out?

03:23.324 --> 03:24.922
You mean he strangled him?

03:25.022 --> 03:26.168
No, that's different.

03:26.235 --> 03:27.968
Uh, evidently, when you choke somebody out,

03:28.035 --> 03:30.282
you cut off their blood
supply, and they pass out.

03:30.368 --> 03:31.212
Pass out?

03:31.251 --> 03:33.168
That's the way you gain
control or whatever.

03:33.235 --> 03:34.402
"Gain control"?

03:34.468 --> 03:36.573
How do you know all this, Ted?

03:38.235 --> 03:39.768
The senator told me.

03:41.116 --> 03:42.468
Anyway, Teddy told the Sheriff,

03:42.535 --> 03:45.268
and he, the Sheriff,
told the senator, and...

03:45.999 --> 03:47.087
And so on.

03:50.377 --> 03:52.768
I didn't want to have to
tell you this, Janet.

03:55.361 --> 03:56.881
I'm gonna make some coffee.

03:57.979 --> 03:59.243
Come down when you're dressed.

